  "summary": "Postinstall beacon exfiltrates host and username to hardcoded oastify.com collector",
  "details": "package.json declares a postinstall hook that runs mw.js on npm install. mw.js reads os.hostname() and os.userInfo().username and issues an HTTPS GET to a hardcoded Burp Collaborator subdomain (gdx35zc4m7hymba6asotmwhd349vxlla.oastify.com), passing the collected identifiers as query parameters. The destination is not configurable, is unrelated to any stated package function, and fires automatically at install time.",
